{"tid":51011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"狗公同公廁雞一齊簡直絕配？","createTime":"2016-12-23T00:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T08:45:28.000Z","uid":26909,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"177e1930418505c0c1c34da6966c5abeb5738cd8","tid":51011,"uid":26909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T00:55:36.000Z","msg":"講之前戴翻個頭盔先<br />\n我係嚟派花生㗎咋<br />\n花生高唔高汁就見仁見智喇<br />\n當吹下水大家討論下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L1u5244.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL1u5244.jpg&h=1f956948&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b657e44f58626dc22ece53c1b34e5894e94797ba","tid":51011,"uid":26909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:07:24.000Z","msg":"男主有三個 女主有一個<br />\n<br />\n先講A君喇，A就係條女嘅exex嚟嘅<br />\n條女同B君拍緊拖個時就上A君屋企瞓<br />\n<br />\n後尾條女有咗bb<br />\n<br />\n*問題嚟喇*<br />\n大家覺得個bb會係邊個嘅？點解會咁覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後條女落咗個bb之後同B君分咗手喇<br />\n注*B君有出錢比條女落bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後C君出現了<br />\n條女就同咗C君一齊<br />\nC君就成日係fb開po話見到B君就見一次打一次<br />\n但每次C君見到B君個時又收曬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到好威豬咁要保護條女但次次都淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地嚟睇下條女講過啲咩先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxd169O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgxd169O.jpg&h=892ba9c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5M6LRwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5M6LRwq.jpg&h=eef51e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得B君好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戴咗咁大頂<span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span>仲要比人當水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔知大家點睇成件事呢</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2753345baabe04dfbd8663a65ebccf072b6b412","tid":51011,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:10:07.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"458ade0488fba61cf6b3fd6c3cfeead24c84adb1","tid":51011,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:11:34.000Z","msg":"冇睇<br />\n不過狗公同公廁最好死埋一二邊過世<br />\n唔好阻住個地球轉"},{"pid":"5982c84bb495f184040fb77718188831c6e20996","tid":51011,"uid":26909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇睇<br />\n不過狗公同公廁最好死埋一二邊過世<br />\n唔好阻住個地球轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd13e74070d0079d44bcbd55d999d781988d817","tid":51011,"uid":24063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"最尾露撚左條女個樣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8676f0ef18dce8421d2d429c15bab3984b9c6d56","tid":51011,"uid":4329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:13:04.000Z","msg":"有男朋友仲搞三搞四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc557c56271054155f92ee0de53d1bdc2dbc7eff","tid":51011,"uid":26909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾露撚左條女個樣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不撚小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow